theorem dense_iff_interior_closure_eq_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    Dense A ↔ interior (closure A) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hDense
    exact interior_closure_eq_univ_of_dense (A := A) hDense
  · intro hInt
    have hClosure : (closure A : Set X) = (Set.univ : Set X) :=
      (interior_closure_eq_univ_iff (A := A)).1 hInt
    simpa [Dense] using hClosure
